data.description: Welcome home to the heart of the Poconos where you will enjoy privacy and comfort on a sprawling 1.03-acre corner lot. This contemporary 2/3 bedroom, 2 full bath home offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. Step into the vaulted living room, adorned with natural light and a charming brick fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings or cozy evenings. The adjacent formal dining room sets the stage for gatherings and dinners, while the updated kitchen steals the spotlight with its two-tone shaker-style cabinets, an expansive center island with storage and seating – a chef's delight! The first floor boasts a convenient full bathroom and a separate large laundry room that serves as a versatile space, doubling as an office or craft room with outside access. Upstairs, the master bedroom awaits, providing a private retreat with seamless access to the main bathroom. A thoughtfully designed loft leads to the second bedroom, offering flexibility for your needs. Step outside onto your deck, perfect for entertaining or enjoying a quiet morning coffee. Additionally, there is a circular driveway and storage shed that adds functionality and convenience to the property.This home is situated in the Woodale Country Acres Community, and the best part – no HOA fees! Commuting is a breeze, and you're surrounded by all the attractions the Poconos have to offer. Embrace the lifestyle you've always dreamed of in this contemporary gem!
